title: Five Iron Frenzy - Engine of a Million Plots (VBR) [RE-SEEDED]
description:
FIVE IRON FRENZY - ENGINE OF A MILLION PLOTS [2013]
Now with more seeds!

Five Iron Frenzy's first album in 10 years, ENGINE OF A MILLION PLOTS.
Some of the songs are from the sampler given out at the shows in real 320kbps, but the others (*) are ripped at 256kbps from Spotify (the ID3 tags say '320' but were transcoded to save quality).

2  - So Far
3  - Zen & The Art of Xenophobia
4  - We Own The Skies*
5  - Someone Else's Problem*
6  - I Am Jack's Smirking Revenge*
7  - To Start a Fire*
8  - Battle Dancing Unicorns With Glitter
9  - Into Your Veins
10 - It Was A Dark & Stormy Night
11 - I've Seen The Sun*
12 - Blizzards & Bygones*
13 - God Hates Flags (B-Side)

ENJOY.
